{"tid":1331483,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"注意!! 請廣傳! 呼籲大家提醒/ 澄清身邊親朋戚友","createTime":"2019-07-19T03:05:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T07:01:09.000Z","uid":92347,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e2445de82eb359608e61f94b6686b72bff75bc53","tid":1331483,"uid":92347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T03:05:16.000Z","msg":"注意! <br />\n<br />\n20號星期六有支持政府及黑警集會, 中共勢力吹緊雞<br />\n1) 多間中共背景公司命令/呼籲 下屬員工出席20號<br />\n2) 多區連儂牆, 被人以&quot;愛香港&quot;等混淆字句海報，宣傳720集會<br />\n3) 今早凌晨2/3點, 有過百戴口罩講普通話人士，係大埔連儂隧道被破壞，並且貼上720混淆字句海報<br />\n4) 有長者手機收到短訊，呼籲長者出席720集會(內容不提支持政府/黑警)<br />\n5) 720 由多個親共組織發起遊行，召集人黃英豪 身兼全國政協委員 <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">在此呼籲大家提醒/ 澄清身邊親朋戚友 <br />\n720主題是親政府支持警察暴力執法<br />\n避免誤會，勿去720, 特別係無睇連登既人</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">同時有能力請印列721宣傳品，係各區/ 交通工具/ 多人地方貼上</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n721(星期日) 有民陣大遊行<br />\n下午 3 時在銅鑼灣維園集合起步，遊行至遮打道終審法院結束。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/29MHQRn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F29MHQRn.jpg&h=92beabbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YkF16pH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYkF16pH.jpg&h=6c558bc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C99RKbo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC99RKbo.jpg&h=5cdc0e27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D1JZS4J.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD1JZS4J.png&h=733f5807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xt6TXwo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxt6TXwo.png&h=8fe1e052&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8GPyc4J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8GPyc4J.jpg&h=458bbf5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/